ested reviewers\n\n- laurent22\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- walkthrough_end -->\n\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>🚥 Pre-merge checks | ✅ 4</summary>\n\n<details>\n<summary>✅ Passed checks (4 passed)</summary>\n\n|               Check name              | Status   | Explanation                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |\n| :-----------------------------------: | :------- | :---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|              Title check              | ✅ Passed | The title clearly and specifically describes the main fix: addressing a Markdown export issue where folders differing only in special characters were losing data through overwriting.                                                    |\n|           Description check           | ✅ Passed | The description is directly relevant to the changeset, explaining the problem, solution, validation approach, and manual testing steps for the folder deduplication fix.                                                                  |\n|           Docstring Coverage          | ✅ Passed | No functions found in the changed files to evaluate docstring coverage. Skipping docstring coverage check.                                                                                                                                |\n| Pr Description Must Follow Guidelines | ✅ Passed | The pull request description includes all required sections per the contribution guidelines, clearly describing the user-impact problem, providing a high-level solution explanation, and documenting the test plan with passing results. |\n\n</details>\n\n<